        <updateDate>2022-09-22T10:10:04Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Make Russia Pay Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of the Treasury to liquidate all Russian assets seized by the United States and deposit the resulting funds into a Ukrainian Humanitarian Aid Fund established by the bill. Treasury may use the funds to provide assistance to Ukraine, including by providing funding to Ukraine's government for humanitarian and security assistance. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
